# FB_EVENTOS code owners.
#
# Repository owner reviews everything by default until additional collaborators
# join. Replace the placeholder handle with your GitHub username after the
# repository is pushed to GitHub (README "Repository setup" section tracks
# this as a follow-up).
#
# Higher-specificity rules override earlier ones (last match wins per GitHub
# CODEOWNERS semantics).

# Catch-all default owner (placeholder — update after first push).
*       @REPO_OWNER_PLACEHOLDER

# Security-sensitive paths get the same single owner today; split as the team
# grows.
/.github/workflows/   @REPO_OWNER_PLACEHOLDER
/scripts/ci/          @REPO_OWNER_PLACEHOLDER
/docker/              @REPO_OWNER_PLACEHOLDER
/.gitleaks.toml       @REPO_OWNER_PLACEHOLDER
